review_text: Small park that is friendly for kids and they can cool down with the water as well.

(Translated by Google) Very beautiful park in the Lachine borough, accessible on foot, by bike, by car, by bus, by scooter ... a pedestrian bridge gives access to boul. St-Joseph along the river and its cycle path. There is a shelter for show and exhibition. The Lachine Harmony will perform its practices on Tuesday evenings and probably concerts on some Sunday afternoons.

(Original)
Très beau parc dans l'arrondissement Lachine, accessible à pied, à vélo,  en auto, en autobus,  en trottinette...un pont piétonnier donne accès au boul. St-Joseph  en bordure du fleuve et de sa piste cyclable.  Il y a un abri pour spectacle et exposition.  L'Harmonie de Lachine fera ses pratiques les mardis soir et probablement des concerts certains dimanche après-midi.

(Translated by Google) Very nice park including a bike path along the Lachine Canal. Too bad dogs are not allowed.

(Original)
Tres beau parc incluant une piste cyclable le long du canal Lachine. Dommage les chiens n'y sont pas admis.
